**Stream Types**:
```javascript
const { Readable, Writable, Transform, Duplex } = require('stream');

// Readable stream
class Counter extends Readable {
  constructor(options) {
    super(options);
    this.max = 10;
    this.index = 1;
  }

  _read() {
    const i = this.index++;
    if (i > this.max) {
      this.push(null); // End of stream
    } else {
      this.push(i.toString());
    }
  }
}
```

**Writable Stream**:
